Key Features

  • Pulse Rate Indicator
A complete automatic measuring function with personalized inflation level offered by the JSB Deluxe Upper Arm BP Monitor enables you to measure and monitor your blood pressure efficiently. The JSB BP monitor also features an Irregular heartbeat indicator that detects abnormal heartbeats while your pressure is being measured.

The JSB deluxe arm BP monitor has been evaluated and proven to meet the rigorous safety and accuracy standards set by CE FDA and RoHS.

Build

Crafted to meet comfort ease of use and simplicity all at the same time this digital JSB arm BP monitor offers a simple and user friendly control panel. The control panel is made up of a large and clear LCD display and easy to operate control buttons.

The BP monitor comes with an easy-wrap cuff that naturally conforms to the contours of your arms. The BP monitor provides a medium sized cuff with a circumference ranging from 22 to 32 cm which auto inflates to an optimal level. The process of operating the BP monitor is very simple and comfortable. All you need to do is attach the cuff to your arms and press the button to get your digital readings.

Performance and Features

The digital deluxe arm BP monitor by JSB utilizes a digital sensor that uses a fuzzy logic technology to detect your pulse signals. This enables automatic inflation and deflation of the cuff resulting to accurate readings and a shorter measurement time. This deluxe upper arm blood pressure monitor is also equipped with a memory function that allows two users to capture 180 readings displayed with an updated date and time. You can use the memory bank for checking the variations of your BP measurements in order to get a better understanding of your blood pressure condition.

The deluxe digital arm blood pressure monitor by JSB simultaneously displays digital readings of both systolic/ diastolic pressure and pulse rates. The BP monitor is capable of displaying readings ranging from 0 to 300 mmHg for blood pressure and 40 to 199 beats/minute for pulse rates. Quick and accurate this digital deluxe arm BP monitor is calibrated at +/-3 mmHg for pressure readings and +/-5% of reading for pulse progress. This JSB BP monitor functions soundly with a power supply of 4 AA batteries.
